    <title><![CDATA[OSX Configration]]></title>
    <link href="blog.bruceleo1969.xyz/2015/8/5/Mac/"/>
    <id>blog.bruceleo1969.xyz/2015/8/5/Mac/</id>
    <published>2015-08-05T10:40:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-08-05T12:46:25.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://7xku3r.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/15-8-5/97347738.jpg" class="img-topic"></p>
<p>Personalized Settings for my mac .</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h2 id="Security">Security</h2><p>For some reasons i don’t want anyone knows my existence so as my computer . The Netbois function should be closed for avoiding network scanning . There are two ways to make it achieved .</p>
<ul>
<li>Cancel the execute privilege :</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># chmod 000 /usr/sbin/netbiosd</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>Deny all the connections of netbios by <strong>Little Snitch</strong><br><img src="http://7xku3r.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/15-8-5/72876707.jpg" alt=""></li>
</ul>
<p>Obviously , the first method is best .</p>
<h2 id="Adobe">Adobe</h2><p>Poverty is always the excuses for using pirated software , although i paid for softwares sometimes but i can’t really pay the bill of adobe_series_software .</p>
<p>I’m blamed for cracking PS 、AE 、PR 、AU and so on . Sorry Adobe .</p>
<p>But , how to keep your adobe software safe when VPN is connected ? We all know that the hosts file will not be used when VPN is working .</p>
<p>Two same methods as advices above :</p>
<ul>
<li>Cancel the execute privilege of the verify software :</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># chmod 000 /Applications/Utilities/Adobe\ Application\ Manager/P7/adobe_licutil.app/Contents/MacOS/adobe_licutil</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>Ban all the data transfer of the verify software via <strong>Little Snith</strong></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="UninstallPKG">UninstallPKG</h2><p>It’s not an easy job to uninstall the .pkg file we install at our mac if the uninstall program is not provided . But with the help of <strong>UninstallPKG</strong> you can uninstall every pkg file easily .</p>
<p>First , we have to crack it … Orz …</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ open /User/user_name/Library/Preferences/com.corecode.UninstallPKG.plist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Find the key <code>Usage</code> and change it’s value into <code>-99999999999</code> .</p>
<p><img src="http://7xku3r.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/15-8-5/71479203.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="Little_Snitch">Little Snitch</h2><p>Yeah , this program is a powerful weapon exactly . It provides us the power to make sure that every very data transfer under our own control .</p>
<p>Somehow , we have to crack it also for it’s extreme high price .</p>
<p>An available key below :</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">33</span>R7LM0U00-<span class="number">715</span>JZ-<span class="number">95</span>RYHBCFTU</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="http://7xku3r.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/15-8-5/64742615.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p><del>NOT YET FINISHED</del></p>
]]></content>
